lead_paragraph: Struggling for money and reeling from successive scandals, two groups of newly appointed leaders of American football have travelled to Switzerland in the hope of reviving their once important influence on the sport's governing body, FIFA.

headline.print_headline: The Americas Look to Reassert Their Influence Within FIFA
headline.main: The Americas Look to Reassert Their Influence Within FIFA
